    slug: "how-to-setup-iptv-on-tivimate-iptv-player",
    title: "How to setup IPTV on TiviMate IPTV Player?",
    description: null,
    body: "<p><strong>TiviMate IPTV Player Overview</strong></p><p>TiviMate IPTV Player is an Android-based application used to watch IPTV content. It supports both remote playlists and the Xtream Codes API system. It's a popular choice for streaming IPTV channels on Firestick devices.</p><p><strong>How to Add IPTV Channels to TiviMate Using Xtream Codes</strong></p><p>In this guide, we'll walk you through the steps to add IPTV channels to the TiviMate IPTV Player using the Xtream Codes API. At the end, we'll also highlight some of the app’s key features, including Catch-Up, Recording, Subtitles, and more.</p><p><strong>Setting Up TiviMate IPTV Player via Xtream Codes API</strong></p><p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Download and install the TiviMate app from the Google Play Store:<br><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ar.tvplayer.tv\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ar.tvplayer.tv</a></p><p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Once the app is open, click on <strong>\"ADD PLAYLIST\"</strong> to begin.</p><img src=\"https://iptvkb.com/storage/article_images/1893af3f-b92a-4a3a-9905-a21cfe0e12cd.jpg\"><p><strong>Step 3:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 48, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> Click on “</span><strong>Xtream Codes login</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 48, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">” and them </span><strong>Next</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 48, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">.</span></p><img src=\"https://iptvkb.com/storage/article_images/4490fb83-2777-49e1-a3bf-36d67564a9e9.jpg\"><p><strong>Step 4:</strong><br>Enter the <strong>Server Address</strong>, <strong>Username</strong>, and <strong>Password</strong> — these details can be extracted from your M3U URL.</p><p>Most modern IPTV providers offer a user dashboard where you can easily access your M3U link and retrieve this information.</p><p><strong>Need help finding your Server Address, Username, and Password?</strong><br>Simply refer to your M3U URL format or check your IPTV provider's dashboard.</p><p>If you want access to Video on Demand (VOD) content, make sure to enable the <strong>“Include VOD”</strong> option.</p><img src=\"https://iptvkb.com/storage/article_images/cf9019f5-887a-42eb-b8a6-87eac426486a.jpg\"><p>Proceed, and after a short moment, your channels will load and appear.</p><hr><p><strong>TiviMate IPTV Player Features</strong></p><p>TiviMate offers a variety of useful features designed to enhance your IPTV experience. Some of the key features include:</p><ul><li><p>A modern user interface optimized for large screens</p></li><li><p>EPG (Electronic Program Guide) with scheduled updates</p></li><li><p>Auto-start on device boot</p></li><li><p>Ability to mark and access favorite channels</p></li><li><p>Picture-in-Picture (PiP) support</p></li><li><p>Catch-up TV functionality</p></li><li><p>Channel recording options</p></li></ul><p>Once you open a channel, you'll see the playback interface. To view the program guide, simply click on <strong>\"TV Guide\"</strong>.</p><img src=\"https://iptvkb.com/storage/article_images/13565b27-7b06-4435-97da-65ebff2d029a.jpg\"><p><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 48, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">By holding the “</span><strong>OK</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 48, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">” button for 2 seconds you can see the setting menu, here you can see many features like Recording.</span></p><img src=\"https://iptvkb.com/storage/article_images/3d8cf228-0894-4bc8-89c6-57714ffcccda.jpg\"><p><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 48, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Scroll right a little and you will see other options like subtitle enable “CC” or “Add to Favorites” .</span></p><img src=\"https://iptvkb.com/storage/article_images/6cff447e-f881-4731-8961-2f3cc163ddc6.jpg\"><p>At the end right click on “<strong>Setting</strong>” to see more options.</p><p><br></p><img src=\"https://iptvkb.com/storage/article_images/aa4a0f4f-f55f-49f7-901e-48b5ead9ab1c.jpg\"><img src=\"https://iptvkb.com/storage/article_images/0dae5599-462e-438d-8ff3-bc0941eb8ce8.jpg\">",
    views: 392,
    updatedAt: "2026-06-23 08:13:57",
    category: "android",
